    ...          ${fileName}
    ...          ${startBlock}
    ...          ${endBlock}
    ...          ${fileLength}
    ...          ${lastModified}
    ...          ${clusterType}
    ${didRead} =  cache Data Using Client File System For Node
    ...  ${host}
    ...  ${fileName}
    ...  ${startBlock}
    ...  ${endBlock}
    ...  ${fileLength}
    ...  ${lastModified}
    ...  ${clusterType}
    SHOULD BE TRUE  ${didRead}

